Voters in different polling units along College Road, Ifako/Ijaiye area of Lagos are still awaiting arrival of electoral officers as soldiers have mounted road blocks along the popular highway. Men of Operation MESA are seen patrolling the road while a truck conveying cows from the north, heading to the Agege Abattoir area has just been detained at the College bus stop end of the road. Ifako/Ijaiye‎ bye-election: voting ends, counting begins Ifako/Ijaiye bye-election: Traffic glitches as restriction ‎order takes effect Kogi Guber election records smooth accreditation